org.openwms.common.location.api

  • Packages that use org.openwms.common.location.api 
    Package Description
    org.openwms.common.location
    This package contains all types to describe locations.
    org.openwms.common.location.api
    This package contains the public API to deal with Locations and LocationGroups.
    org.openwms.common.location.api.events
    This package contains event typed belonging to the public API.
    org.openwms.common.location.impl
    This package contains internal implementation classes.
    org.openwms.common.location.spi
    This package contains types for extenstion points and hooks (SPI - Service Provider Interface)
    org.openwms.common.transport.api
    This package contains the public API to deal with TransportUnits.
